# Master Handoff Prompt: Obsidian Logic Marketing System (SaaS Rewrite)

**Objective for AI Assistant (Claude/Cursor):**
I need you to analyze two existing codebases in my workspace and merge their best features into a unified, multi-tenant SaaS application. We are transforming my existing "LinkedIn Post Generator v1.1" and integrating features from "Keith's Assessment Tool" (a LinkedIn intelligence platform).

This is a massive refactoring and feature-building effort. Because of the complexity, I have broken the implementation plan down into **6 Highly Detailed Phases**. 

## Global Architecture Rules
1. **Backend:** Python FastAPI ([server.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/Documents/Keith%20Assesment%20Tool/Antigravity_Linkedin_Assessment%20%20clean/LinkedIn%20Post%20Generator%20v1.1/server.py)) serving both API routes and static frontend files.
2. **Auth & Data Layer:** Firebase Authentication + Firestore Database (document-oriented, perfect for SaaS multi-tenancy).
3. **Execution Layer:** Python scripts in [execution/](file:///c:/Users/Hp/Documents/Keith%20Assesment%20Tool/__MACOSX/Antigravity_Linkedin_Assessment%20%20clean/._execution) orchestrated by [orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/Hp/Documents/Keith%20Assesment%20Tool/Antigravity_Linkedin_Assessment%20%20clean/LinkedIn%20Post%20Generator%20v1.1/orchestrator.py) via subprocesses. Highly deterministic.
4. **Frontend:** Vanilla ES6 Javascript SPA.
5. **Intelligence Engines:** Gemini 3.0 API (core generation), Apify (surveillance/research), Firecrawl (brand extraction).

